{"tid":1727963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「戰術」兵種一定要提升","createTime":"2019-11-16T16:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T02:28:56.000Z","uid":133569,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5f24bb93a8786611a40398474312ceb46a4edcf7","tid":1727963,"uid":133569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T16:01:31.000Z","msg":"而加大家軍力根本一直都唔夠，雖然升級左魔法師但兩軍攻擊距離差太遠，再打落去唔會有反勝機會。<br />\n<br />\n早兩日當有人首次練成弓兵對方即刻大為緊張就知道方向正確。所以大家一定要再升級做弓兵同埋要大量搵資源造弓。<br />\n<br />\n當有左攻擊距離防守力自然大增，對家一定唔敢再隨便進攻。<br />\n<br />\n要打低帝王時代既中國，仍然只係黑暗時代既大家，一定要盡快升級啊！出弓啦！打AOC既各位！！！"},{"pid":"e2a7c38ff71154b01336191f5f994d05cbc277dd","tid":1727963,"uid":258373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T16:12:56.000Z","msg":"No clue what AOC is but ok<br />\nGive me that urgency<br />\n#TimeToGetPersonal"},{"pid":"d3f9fa89833b7c1ac698e58932b22b836e6721c3","tid":1727963,"uid":133569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T16:30:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04b6f1c17fe06886443d70d0695708cd012199d6","tid":1727963,"uid":133569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:28:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fb7fd23ce0543fcc692c6bcf5171a3c8c7017c2","tid":1727963,"uid":133569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:12:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70ff7177f9fbfe2e28644487570caccdd22fa11c","tid":1727963,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:22:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d4f5158a8b67b7651bf66644d02532f9132a1c1","tid":1727963,"uid":133569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T02:28:56.000Z","msg":"推"}]}